title: #733 - Joey Diaz on Two of His Most Important Friendships
description:
Joey Diaz talks about Jorge Masvidal's growth as a man from his appearance on The Church to beating Nate Diaz at UFC 244. Joey also discusses two of the most important friendships he's had.
